           rolemaps-to="P"
          >
         <?MarkedContent page="1" ?>We’re surrounded! [Estragon makes a rush towards back.] Imbe
         <?MarkedContent page="1" ?>cile! There’s no way out there. [He takes Estragon by the arms and drags him towards front. Gesture towards front.] There! Not a soul in sight! Off you go! Quick! [He pushes Estragon towards auditorium. Estragon recoils in horror.] You won’t? [He contemplates auditorium.] Well I can under
         <?MarkedContent page="1" ?>stand that. Wait till I see. [He reflects.] Your only hope left is to disappear. (47)
        </text>
